    {
        "Key": 19,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员无帽",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "你和米拉是怎么认识的？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 20,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "陶",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc31ep10_npc003_04",
        "zh_CN": "米拉的姐姐薇奈特和我认识很久了。我的治疗方案最初就是由她构思的。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 21,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "陶",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc31ep10_npc003_05",
        "zh_CN": "生下克罗瑞娜不久后，她就去世了。从那之后，就由米拉接替她的位置。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 22,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "陶的表情有一丝不寻常的地方。往常看到我的时候，她会有开心、欣慰之类的情绪，通过微笑、点头、展眉等微表情透露出来。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 23,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "而现在……我总觉得有点假装的成分。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 24,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "灵光一闪——",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 25,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员无帽",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "答应我，别逞强。有事情就让我来解决。",
        "disable": 0
    },
